Yep.

46:51.642 --> 46:52.977
For the rest
of your life?

46:55.313 --> 46:57.064
That is correct.

46:57.064 --> 46:58.190
Yeah.

46:58.190 --> 46:59.400
You know,
I'm not a dermatologist,

46:59.400 --> 47:01.527
but that can't be
too good.

47:01.527 --> 47:05.072
