you're working on?

47:21.172 --> 47:22.340
♪ <i>Won't admit the bluff</i> ♪

47:22.340 --> 47:23.758
♪ <i>Sweet</i> ♪
[ Keys clacking ]

47:23.758 --> 47:25.593
Hello?

47:25.593 --> 47:26.969
♪ <i>This candy gives me luck</i> ♪

47:26.969 --> 47:28.012
♪ <i>Sweet</i> ♪

47:28.012 --> 47:29.680
♪ <i>Can't get enough</i> ♪

47:29.680 --> 47:31.390
