47:31.390 --> 47:32.600
You get screwed over once.

47:32.600 --> 47:33.726
You're just gonna lie here
and cry about it,

47:33.726 --> 47:34.935
or are you actually
gonna do something?

47:34.935 --> 47:36.520
They took my idea.

47:36.520 --> 47:38.397
So you only have
one good idea?

47:38.397 --> 47:39.899
♪♪

47:39.899 --> 47:42.234
[ Scoffs ]

47:42.234 --> 47:44.403
