you really <i>are</i> screwed.

47:44.403 --> 47:47.114
♪ <i>I can't resist</i>
<i>his sweet praise</i> ♪

47:47.114 --> 47:48.366
♪ <i>No, no</i> ♪

47:48.366 --> 47:51.327
♪ <i>Wrapped up in a sugar rush</i> ♪

47:51.327 --> 47:52.244
[ Door closes ]

47:52.244 --> 47:54.163
