[ Chuckles ]

49:32.970 --> 49:34.972
[ Train whistle blows
in distance ]

49:37.683 --> 49:40.102
I saw your speech.

49:40.102 --> 49:42.229
I thought you'd be in México
by now.

49:42.229 --> 49:45.065
Oh.
I got a place in town.

49:47.693 --> 49:51.405
The truth is,
this is my home now.

49:51.405 --> 49:54.658
I wanted to be a teacher when
I first came here with Rosa.

49:55.868 --> 49:57.578
That was my dream.

49:57.578 --> 49:59.705
I know.

49:59.705 --> 50:02.041
I have a new dream now.

50:04.043 --> 50:05.503
I'm gonna see it through.

50:08.088 --> 50:09.507
What about you?

50:09.507 --> 50:11.217
What are you
gonna do now?

50:12.676 --> 50:13.886
I don't know.

50:17.181 --> 50:19.517
Well, if you're looking
for a job,

50:19.517 --> 50:22.686
my new business partner and I
are hiring.

50:28.150 --> 50:30.319
I'll give you a dozen rows
to cultivate.

50:30.319 --> 50:33.113
It's not much,
but it'll be your show.

50:36.242 --> 50:39.245
You can grow
what you want.

50:39.245 --> 50:41.205
Be your own wine maker.

50:43.749 --> 50:49.880
♪♪

50:49.880 --> 50:51.382
[ Sighs ]

50:51.382 --> 50:55.970
♪♪

50:55.970 --> 50:59.390
♪ <i>La huasteca esta de luto</i> ♪

50:59.390 --> 51:08.732
♪ <i>Se murió su huapanguero</i> ♪

51:08.732 --> 51:12.111
♪ <i>Ya no se oye aquel falsete</i> ♪

51:12.111 --> 51:13.195
Young Margaret: Joe?

51:13.195 --> 51:14.280
♪ <i>Que es el alma del trovero</i> ♪

51:14.280 --> 51:15.698
Joe?

51:15.698 --> 51:21.537
♪♪

51:21.537 --> 51:22.788
Hey.

51:22.788 --> 51:25.916
♪ <i>Rogaciano se llamaba</i> ♪

51:25.916 --> 51:27.543
Hey.

51:27.543 --> 51:29.587
I spoke to my father.

51:29.587 --> 51:31.463
I'd like you to sit down
with him.

51:34.091 --> 51:36.051
I don't think
that's a good idea.

51:36.051 --> 51:37.428
What?

51:37.428 --> 51:38.804
Please?

51:38.804 --> 51:45.936
♪ <i>Las canciones del trovero</i> ♪

51:45.936 --> 51:48.480
♪ <i>La Azucena y la Cecilia</i> ♪

51:48.480 --> 51:49.523
Please.

51:49.523 --> 51:52.484
♪ <i>Lloran, lloran sin consuelo</i> ♪

51:52.484 --> 51:56.155
♪ <i>Malagueña Salerosa</i> ♪

51:56.155 --> 51:57.072
♪ <i>Ya se fue</i> ♪

