52:16.675 --> 52:19.678
I told him, that's not the only
thing you have in common.

52:19.678 --> 52:24.975
♪ <i>Hoy comienza la molienda</i> ♪

52:24.975 --> 52:26.810
There's a fallow tract of land
on the eastern edge

52:26.810 --> 52:28.187
of the vineyard.

52:30.356 --> 52:32.441
I've never been able
to make a profit on it,

52:32.441 --> 52:34.276
but, uh...

52:34.276 --> 52:39.865
♪ <i>Y suspira en cada vuelta</i> ♪

52:39.865 --> 52:43.077
...maybe I just haven't found
the right man for the job.

52:43.077 --> 52:46.664
♪ <i>Por los verdes cafetales</i> ♪

52:46.664 --> 52:55.464
♪ <i>Más allá de aquel potrero</i> ♪

52:55.464 --> 52:58.384
<i>Pues,</i> Mr. Honeycroft,

52:58.384 --> 52:59.510
I'm your man.

52:59.510 --> 53:07.935
♪ <i>Se aparece el huapanguero</i> ♪

53:07.935 --> 53:11.230
♪ <i>La Azucena y la Cecilia</i> ♪

53:11.230 --> 53:14.441
♪ <i>Lloran, lloran sin consuelo</i> ♪

53:14.441 --> 53:17.736
♪ <i>Malagueña Salerosa</i> ♪

53:17.736 --> 53:19.405
You don't need to do this.

53:19.405 --> 53:21.073
You don't need to go.

53:21.073 --> 53:22.574
No.

53:22.574 --> 53:24.243
I think it's for the best,
Lettie.

53:26.787 --> 53:28.414
You need time.

53:30.708 --> 53:32.584
But know I will never stop
loving you.

53:32.584 --> 53:40.801
♪ <i>Rogaciano el huapanguero</i> ♪

